         <abstract id="aspace_d5e64f5632e08be0f5a6b6f7b24a21ed">The papers consist of manuscript drafts of George Vernadsky's published books and articles on Russian history. Also included in the papers are photostats of documents used by Vernadsky in his research and writing.</abstract>
